This assignment is written in C language. It can be complied using gcc
on terminal, on xcode or any other compiler. After running it, press
any of the following keys to enable the property.

Pressing c/C clears the screen and the data structure and can start
from fresh.

Esc leads to the termination of the command.

Key - Property

p/P - Points
l/L - Line
t/T - Triangle
q/Q - Quadrilatral
o/O - Polygon
g/G - Line Loop
s/S - Line Strip
r/R - Triangle Fan
c/C - Clear Screen
Esc - Close

